HEADWORD: Flea-louse
<hw>Flea"-louse`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A jumping plant louse of the family <fam>Psyllid⟦ae⟧</fam>, of many
species. That of the pear tree is <spn>Psylla pyri</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

